A simple and responsive PC Store website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
This project showcases PC components, allows users to browse products, and proceed to a checkout page.

Features

Clean and modern UI

Product listing for PC components

“Buy Now” button redirects to checkout page

Responsive layout for different screen sizes

Easy to customize and extend

Technologies Used

HTML5 – Structure of the website

CSS3 – Styling and layout

JavaScript – Basic interactivity

License

This project is open for educational use and personal learning.